<fieldset>
<legend><%=l(:add_skill_legend)%></legend>
<p>Any skills you add on here should be specific and technical (a language, framework, etc.)  Personal qualities (assertive, client-facing, etc.) are covered in personal qualities, and any further details should be covered in your portfolio or in Three Questions. </p>
<ul>
